      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Down \u0027n\u0027 Dirty",
        "Client": "Distressed Farmer",
        "Description": "Doggone Almudron! That thing\r\ncame through the farm slingin\u0027\r\nits mud all over the dern place.\r\nNow there\u0027s mud all over my dern\r\ncrops. All in my dern house. Heck,\r\neven got mud in my dern pants!\r\nWell, least the Poogies is happy...",
        "Target": "Hunt an Almudron",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "\u00C0 boue de forces",
        "Client": "Fermier en d\u00E9tresse",
        "Description": "Fichu Almudron ! V\u0027l\u00E0-t\u0027y-pas\r\nqu\u0027il a mis d\u0027la boue\r\nd\u0027partout ! Mes r\u00E9coltes, ma\r\nmaison, mon pantalon, j\u0027ai\r\nd\u0027la boue jusqu\u0027au cou !\r\nAaah, c\u0027est les Poogies qui\r\ndoivent \u00EAt\u0027 contents !",
        "Target": "Chasser un Almudron",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0 ou temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Gi\u00F9 nel fango",
        "Client": "Contadino stressato",
        "Description": "Dannato Almudron! Quel mostro\r\nha attraversato la fattoria\r\nlasciando fango ovunque. I\r\ncampi ne sono ricoperti, casa\r\nmia ne \u00E8 piena... \u00C8 finito\r\npersino nei pantaloni! Almeno\r\ni Poogie ne sono felici...",
        "Target": "Caccia un Almudron",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Schmutziger Kampf",
        "Client": "Betr\u00FCbter Bauer",
        "Description": "Elender Almudron! Das Ding hat\r\ndie ganze verdammte Farm mit\r\nseinem Schlamm verdreckt. Die\r\nFeldfr\u00FCchte, mein Haus \u2013 \u00FCber-\r\nall Schlamm! Selbst in meiner\r\nHose ist der Dreck! Na, zumin-\r\ndest den Poogies gef\u00E4llt\u0027s...",
        "Target": "Erjage einen Almudron.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "Tierra y barro",
        "Client": "Granjero en apuros",
        "Description": "\u00A1Condenado y sucio Almudron!\r\nHa aparecido uno en la granja\r\ny lo ha dejado todo perdido de\r\nbarro. \u00A1Si hasta me ha entrado\r\npor los pantalones! Los \u00FAnicos\r\nque est\u00E1n en su salsa son los\r\nPoogies...",
        "Target": "Caza un Almudron",
        "Fail": "La recompensa cae a 0\r\no se acaba el tiempo"
      },
      {
        "Language": "RUS",
        "Name": "\u0413\u0440\u044F\u0437\u043D\u044B\u0435 \u043F\u0440\u0438\u0435\u043C\u0447\u0438\u043A\u0438",
